## 🔌 API Endpoints

### Authentication

* POST /auth/register
* POST /auth/login
* POST /auth/confirm
* POST /auth/forgot
* POST /auth/reset

### Quiz Management

* POST /quiz/create
* GET /quiz/{id}
* GET /quiz/list
* PUT /quiz/{id}
* DELETE /quiz/{id}
* POST /quiz/{id}/submit
* GET /quiz/{id}/results

### Analytics

* GET /analytics/teacher
* GET /student/results

### Study Material

* POST /study/upload
* GET /study/list

### Uploads

* POST /upload/file

### Leaderboard

* GET /leaderboard

---

## 🚀 Deployment

Frontend:

* Amazon CloudFront
* Amazon S3

Backend:

* AWS Lambda
* API Gateway
* Serverless Framework

Deployment Command:

```bash
sls deploy
```

